@title Welcome to the `pkt' application!
@doc `pkt' is a pocket URL shortener

== Prerequisites ==

git, GNU make, erlang (tested on 20)

== Usage ==

Run application

`make run'

Web server should be listening on port 8080, e.g. http://localhost:8080

=== Other Usage ===

Run tests

`make tests'

Create docs

`make docs'
